FBIS4-56427 "drlat086_b_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-086 Daily Report 3 May 1994 Haiti Deputies `Urgently' Convened to 3 May Session Deputies `Urgently' Convened to 3 May Session FL0305202994 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio in French 1030 GMT 3 May 94 FL0305202994 Port-au-Prince Signal FM Radio French BFN [Text] Today, the Chamber of Deputies is preparing to meet and discuss the crisis. In a news release, the first secretary of the chamber sends greetings to deputies of the 45th Legislature and urgently solicits their presence at the session scheduled for 3 May at noon. The office of this chamber advises all deputies that at this sociopolitical juncture, their presence is extremely important. This is a release from the Chamber of Deputies.
